        <h2 class="section-title" data-reveal data-delay="1">
          Seven justices.<br /><em>One referendum.</em>
        </h2>
        <p class="section-lede" data-reveal data-delay="2">
          The Supreme Court of Virginia hears <em>Scott v. McDougle</em> with a documented
          4-3 conservative bloc. The four members of that bloc — Kelsey, McCullough,
