          </div>
          <div class="vlaming-takeaway-text">
            <em>Vlaming</em> was an individual-rights culture-war case bounded by
            one teacher and one school district. <em>Scott v. McDougle</em> nullifies
            the express will of <em>1.27 million voters</em> and reshapes federal
            congressional representation for three election cycles. The institutional
            cost is dramatically higher. McCullough especially is reputed to favor
            narrow rulings — and a vote to strike here is anything but narrow.
