              <div class="watch-desc">
                He is the keystone. Watch for any out-of-court speeches,
                law-review work, or amicus invitations that might illuminate his
                thinking. McCullough is not a public-facing justice but he does
                occasionally publish.
              </div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="watch-item" data-reveal data-delay="1">
            <div class="watch-num">02</div>
            <div class="watch-content">
