              </div>
              <div class="watch-desc">
                Judge Lowe's ongoing handling of related issues will give cover
                to a SCOVA strike-down opinion if the eventual ruling tracks his
                reasoning. Movement on Lowe's docket is a leading indicator of
                what shape the upper-court opinion takes.
              </div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="watch-item" data-reveal data-delay="2">
            <div class="watch-num">03</div>
            <div class="watch-content">
