            analysis from public records, not inside information. Reads are most defensible
            for justices with deep public records (Kelsey, McCullough, Powell, Mann)
            and least defensible for justices with thin SCOVA records (Fulton). The
            single biggest analytical risk is over-reading the Vlaming pattern.
            <br /><br />
            <strong>As of 7 May 2026, the court has not ruled.</strong>
